==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*μέχρι, μεχρίς / mechri  mechris / mekh'-ree, mekh-ris'

===Adverb===
'''μεχρι'''
#[[up to|Up to]] (and [[including]]).

*From [[μῆκος]]; as far as, that is, up to a certain point (as preposition of extent [denoting the terminus, whereas [[ἄχρι]]refers especially to the space of time or place intervening] or conjugation): - till, (un-) to, until.

